{"id:": "/div[1]", "tag": "div", "attributes": {"type": "article", "{http://www.w3.org/XML/1998/namespace}id": "MG-1678-05_003", "resp": "mercure"}, "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/head[1]", "tag": "head", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/head[1]/text()[1]", "text": "[Lettre de Tyrsis à Iris, en vers et en prose par M"}, {"id": "/div[1]/head[1]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/head[1]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "r"}], "attributes": {"rend": "sup"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/head[1]/text()[2]", "text": " de Fontenelle]*"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]", "tag": "bibl", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/title[1]", "tag": "title", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/title[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Mercure galant"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/text()[1]", "text": ", mai 1678 [tome 5], p. 3-22."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]", "tag": "quote", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]", "tag": "label", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/text()[1]", "text": "TYRSIS"}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/lb[1]", "tag": "lb", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/text()[2]", "text": "À LA BELLE IRIS."}], "attributes": {"rend": "center"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[1]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Il y a aujourd’huy un peu plus d’un an que je vous ay veuë pour la premiere fois, & par conséquent que je vous aime. C'est une journée trop remarquable, & qui a eu de trop grandes suites, pour l’oublier. Le pourrez-vous croire ? Les Amours l’ont solemnisée ; & comme cette Feste vous regarde, vous auriez sujet de vous plaindre, si je vous en laissois ignorer les particularitez."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[2]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[2]/text()[1]", "text": "Le premier jour de May 1678. on porta un Billet chez tous les Amours. Ils y trouverent ces quatre Vers."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Les Amours sont demain priez d’un grand Disné"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": "Chez l’Amour, Fils d’Iris, autrement la***"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": "Comme c’est le jour qu’il est né,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[4]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[4]/text()[1]", "text": "Il se met en frais, & les traite."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[3]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[3]/text()[1]", "text": "Il vint donc un tres-grand nombre d’Amours chez celuy qui les avoit conviez ; & aussitost qu’il les vit :"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Chers Amours, leur dit-il avec un doux soûris,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": "Nous celebrons une grande journée."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": "C'est aujourd’huy que je suis né d’Iris,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[4]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[4]/text()[1]", "text": "Aujourd’huy je compte une année."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[5]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[5]/text()[1]", "text": "Quoy ? vous n’auriez qu’un an, s’écria-t-on ? Abus !"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[6]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[6]/text()[1]", "text": "Vous paroissez trop grand & trop fort pour vostre âge."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[7]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[7]/text()[1]", "text": "De bonne-foy, dit-il, je n’ay pas d’avantage,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[8]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[8]/text()[1]", "text": "Mais aussi je ne croistray plus."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[9]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[9]/text()[1]", "text": "À peine venois-je de naistre,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[10]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[10]/text()[1]", "text": "Que j’estois déjà grand Amour."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[11]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[11]/text()[1]", "text": "Iris qui me voyait croistre comme le jour,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[12]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[12]/text()[1]", "text": "S'imaginoit que j’allois toûjours croistre ;"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[13]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[13]/text()[1]", "text": "Mais quand on croist si viste, il est un certain point"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[14]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[14]/text()[1]", "text": "Où l’on s’arreste de bonne heure ;"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[15]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[15]/text()[1]", "text": "Ainsi qu’Iris ne s’en étonne point,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[16]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[16]/text()[1]", "text": "Me voilà tel qu’il faut que je demeure."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[4]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[4]/text()[1]", "text": "Apres ce peu de paroles qui furent dites en arrivant, les Amours se mirent à table, & chacun ayant pris place selon son rang,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Le Maistre du Festin leur en fit l’ouverture"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": "Par deux grands Plats que l’on servit."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": "Dans l’un estoient des viandes en peinture,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[4]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[4]/text()[1]", "text": "Dans l’autre des Billets qu’il disoit plein d’esprit."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[5]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[5]/text()[1]", "text": "La plûpart des Amours se mirent en colere."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[6]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[6]/text()[1]", "text": "Quoy, s’écrierent-ils, vous moquez-vous de nous ?"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[7]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[7]/text()[1]", "text": "Viandes creuses, & Billet doux,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[8]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[8]/text()[1]", "text": "Est-ce là le repas que vous voulez nous faire ?"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[9]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[9]/text()[1]", "text": "Hé quoy, reprit leur Hoste, est-ce que mes Billets"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[10]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[10]/text()[1]", "text": "Ne seront pas pour une chere complete ?"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[11]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[11]/text()[1]", "text": "Iris ne me nourrit que de semblables mets,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[12]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[12]/text()[1]", "text": "Je vous traite comme on me traite."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[13]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[13]/text()[1]", "text": "Je ne sçait pas comment il faut vous recevoir,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[14]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[14]/text()[1]", "text": "Si vous n’estes contens de ce qu’on vous présente,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[15]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[15]/text()[1]", "text": "Car moy sans vanité qui crois bien vous valoir,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[16]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[16]/text()[1]", "text": "Il faut bien que je m’en contente."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[17]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[17]/text()[1]", "text": "Presque tous les Amours l’avoient déjà quité,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[18]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[18]/text()[1]", "text": "En pestant contre le régale."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[19]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[19]/text()[1]", "text": "Il estoit seulement resté"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[20]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[20]/text()[1]", "text": "Quelques petits Amours de vie assez frugale,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[21]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[21]/text()[1]", "text": "Lors qu’il dit aux premiers ; revenez sur vos pas,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[22]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[22]/text()[1]", "text": "Je vous feray servir des viandes moins legeres."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[23]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[23]/text()[1]", "text": "Pour moy, vous soufrirez que je n’y touche pas,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[24]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[24]/text()[1]", "text": "Il faut que je m’en tienne à mes mets ordinnaires."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[5]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[5]/text()[1]", "text": "Il parut aussitost un Service dont tous les Amours furent fort satisfaits. Comme leur Hoste mangea fort peu, il s’appliqua à les divertir par son entretien. Il leur apprit que sa naissance avoit esté précedée de quelques Prodiges, car ce n’estoit pas un Amour du commun. Ces Prodiges estoient, que quelque temps avant qu’il nâquist, le feu avoit pris à tous les Livres de Morale qu’avoit son Pere, nommé Tyrsis, jeune Homme qui faisoit fort le Philosophe, & que le Mercure Galant estant apparu une nuit en songe à sa Mere Iris, luy avoit dit ces mots, "}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[5]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[5]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Aime, & je t’immortalise"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[5]/text()[2]", "text": ". La Conversation tourna en suite sur Tyrsis & sur Iris mesmes, & on demanda au Maistre du Festin comment ils estoient ensemble, ou s’il l’aimoit mieux, comment Tyrsis estoit dans l’esprit d’Iris. Voicy sa Réponse."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[4]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[4]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[4]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Ce Tyrsis qui luy rend mille hommages constans,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[4]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[4]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": "Aux despens de son cœur veut qu’elle les achete."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[4]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[4]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": "Iris, qui ne sçauroit desavoüer la debte,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[4]/l[4]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[4]/l[4]/text()[1]", "text": "Pour le payer, luy demande du temps."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[4]/l[5]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[4]/l[5]/text()[1]", "text": "Cependant s’il reçoit une œillade flateuse,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[4]/l[6]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[4]/l[6]/text()[1]", "text": "Et quelques mots douteux qu’il entend comme il veut,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[4]/l[7]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[4]/l[7]/text()[1]", "text": "Il croit que sa fortune est encor trop heureuse,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[4]/l[8]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[4]/l[8]/text()[1]", "text": "Car d’une mêchante Payeuse"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[4]/l[9]", "